<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 119.23 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 5 p.m. (0800 GMT) Thursday, down
2.65 yen from late Wednesday.
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
(WS SL:BC-Yen-Dollar; CT:f; 
(REG:ASIA;)
(REG:ENGL;)
(REG:EURO;)
(REG:BRIT;)
