Off shore seas 4 to 6 ft. Scattered showers. Isolated
thunderstorms.
	   Outlook for Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands waters:
	   Friday night through Monday... Wind northeast to east at 15 to
25 kt. Atlantic seas 6 to 8 ft in northeast swells. Caribbean seas
4 to 6 ft.
