accept a peace plan. YUGOSLAVIA-KOSOVO. Lead has moved. By Dusan
Stojanovic. AP Photo PRI101.
	   AMSTERDAM, Netherlands _ A Bosnian Serb general arrested by NATO
on genocide charges guided the troops that massacred thousands of
Muslims from Srebrenica and dumped them in mass graves, the U.N.
indictment reveals. BOSNIA-WAR CRIMES. Has moved. By Jenifer Chao.
