House called back to vote in December if the Judiciary Committee
approves any articles of impeachment against President Bill
Clinton. US-CLINTON-IMPEACHMENT. Lead expected by 2100 GMT. By
David Espo. AP Photo NPT103.
	   WASHINGTON _ Paintings confiscated from Jews by Nazi Germany,
including works by Picasso and Cezanne, could be returned to prewar
owners or their heirs or auctioned to benefit Holocaust survivors
under guidelines being endorsed Thursday at an international
conference. US-HOLOCAUST CONFERENCE. Lead has moved. News
conference scheduled for 1800 GMT. By Laura Myers. AP Photos
covering.
	   MANILA, Philippines _ Neighbors watch helplessly as a fire rages
through a Manila orphanage on Thursday, killing at least 28 people,
mostly children. PHILIPPINES-ORPHANAGE FIRE. Lead has moved. By
Claro Cortes. AP Photos MLA103, MLA112-114.
	   HARARE, Zimbabwe _ The World Council of Churches opens its
fiftieth anniversary assembly with a multicultural worship service
boycotted by Orthodox delegates from Russia and Greece. Attitudes
toward homosexuality are a major cause of the disruption. WORLD
CHURCHES-OPENING. Lead expected by 2100 GMT. By Richard N. Ostling.
AP Photos covering.
	   CAPE CANAVERAL, Florida _ An alarm goes off inside space shuttle
Endeavour's cockpit minutes before liftoff Thursday, forcing the
U.S. space agency to delay its first space station construction
flight. US-SPACE STATION. Lead expected by 2200 GMT. By Marcia
Dunn. AP Photos KSC109-111.
	   LONDON _ Unwilling to shed blue blood in a hopeless cause,
Britain's hereditary nobles were ready to go quietly from the House
of Lords _ only to get into a fight with the commoner who leads
their party. BRITAIN-LORDS. Lead has moved. By Robert Barr. AP
Photos LON103-104.
	   LOOKING AHEAD: Donors conference on war reconstruction opens in
Zagreb, Croatia, on Friday. Saturday is the third anniversary of
the recapture of Jaffna, Sri Lanka from ethnic Tamil guerrillas;
local elections being held in Nigeria. On Sunday, national
elections scheduled in Gabon.
 &UR; FEATURES:
