<HEADLINE>
With BC-Ukraine-Mine Accident
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Ukraine's government moves to satisfy striking miners' demands &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   KIEV, Ukraine (AP) _ About 40,000 miners across Ukraine
continued their strike Thursday, pushing the government and the
legislature to take steps to meet their demands.
	   Parliament on Thursday overwhelmingly approved a resolution
ordering the Cabinet to speed up repayment of mounting wage arrears
to coal workers by Dec. 15.
