<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Russia-Economy, 4th Ld-Writethru </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Russian prime minister calls for more detailed economic plan
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; EDs: UPDATES with ruble's last record low in 4th graf, World Bank
delegation expected in 8th graf. &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photo MOSB103-104,108 &QL; 
 &UR; By ANNA DOLGOV &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
