<HEADLINE>
Gunpowder explodes at factory, no one hurt
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   MOSCOW (AP) _ Gunpowder exploded at a defense plant in Siberia,
causing extensive damage but causing no injuries, a news report
said.
	   The powerful blast in the Ural Mountains city of Perm took place
late Wednesday night when the plant was empty, the ITAR-Tass news
agency said.
	   The small plant was located in a forest area and did not
threaten any other buildings, the report added.
